# ===========================================
# KEEP THESE ESSENTIAL FILES FOR DEPLOYMENT
# ===========================================
# package.json - KEEP (required for dependencies)
# package-lock.json - KEEP (lock file for exact versions)
# next.config.mjs - KEEP (Next.js configuration)
# tailwind.config.js - KEEP (if exists, for styling)
# postcss.config.mjs - KEEP (PostCSS configuration)
# jsconfig.json - KEEP (JavaScript configuration)
# eslint.config.mjs - KEEP (linting rules)
# README.md - KEEP (main documentation)
# app/ - KEEP (main application code)
# components/ - KEEP (React components)
# lib/ - KEEP (utility libraries and data)
# public/ - KEEP (static assets)
# styles/ - KEEP (if exists, CSS files)

# ===========================================
# NOTES FOR DEPLOYMENT:
# ===========================================
# 1. Environment variables (.env.local) are ignored - configure separately in deployment
# 2. Test files are ignored - not needed in production
# 3. Documentation files are ignored - keep only essential docs
# 4. Build artifacts (.next/, out/) are ignored - will be generated during deployment
# 5. Dependencies (node_modules/) are ignored - will be installed during deployment
